## One Service. Unlimited Languages.

Most churches today face a growing challenge.

Your congregation may include:

* Spanish-speaking families
* Korean-speaking members
* International students
* Refugees and immigrants
* Deaf and hard-of-hearing attendees
* Online viewers from around the world

Traditionally, serving these groups requires hiring interpreters, creating separate language services, purchasing interpretation equipment, or asking volunteers to translate.

Exbabel changes that.

With Exbabel Live Video Translation, a single sermon can be delivered simultaneously in multiple languages through AI-powered voice translation and live captions.

The result is a more welcoming, accessible, and unified church experience.

