# Live AI Voice Translation

## Let People Hear the Message, Not Just Read It

Subtitles help.

Hearing the message in your native language creates a completely different experience.

Exbabel generates natural AI voiceovers in real time, allowing attendees to listen to translated audio while watching the live service.

This creates a more immersive and engaging worship experience than captions alone.

