# Architecture & Technical Overview

## Built for Church Tech Directors

Exbabel Live Video Translation combines real-time AI translation, cloud-scale infrastructure, and low-latency streaming technologies to deliver synchronized multilingual experiences.

### Translation Engine

* Real-time speech recognition
* Live speech-to-speech translation
* AI voice synthesis
* Multi-language processing
* Parallel translation sessions

### Streaming Architecture

* RTMP ingestion
* HLS video delivery
* WebSocket low-latency audio transport
* Real-time caption delivery
* Dynamic synchronization controls

### Cloud Infrastructure

* AWS global infrastructure
* Auto-scaling workloads
* Multi-region deployment support
* Elastic compute resources
* High availability architecture

### Intelligent Synchronization

Exbabel continuously aligns:

* Live video
* AI-generated voiceovers
* Captions
* Viewer playback

to ensure a seamless multilingual viewing experience.

