# Frequently Asked Questions

### Do viewers need to install anything?

No. Viewers simply open the stream and select their preferred language.

### Can attendees switch languages during a service?

Yes. Languages can be changed instantly.

### Does Exbabel replace interpreters?

Many churches use Exbabel as a replacement for traditional interpretation workflows, while others use it to expand language coverage.

### Does it work with our existing livestream?

In most cases, yes. Exbabel integrates with standard RTMP streaming workflows.

### How many languages can be supported?

Multiple languages can run simultaneously from a single source stream.

